    {
      "name": "SignalR Hubs",
      "description": "Endpoints SignalR (WebSocket). O Postman testa o handshake HTTP 'negotiate'. Para testar métodos do Hub (SendMessage, GetDashboard etc.), use um client SignalR (ex: @microsoft/signalr no Node.js).\n\n## ChatHub — /hubs/chat\n### Métodos (Client → Server)\n- `SendMessage(userId: string, message: string)` — Envia mensagem ao MetaAgent\n### Eventos (Server → Client)\n- `Connected` — { connectionId, timestamp }\n- `ProcessingStarted` — { timestamp }\n- `ReceiveMessage` — { content, agentName, agentTier, actions, tools, success, sessionId, timestamp }\n- `ReceiveError` — { error, timestamp }\n\n## GatewayHub — /hubs/gateway\n### Métodos (Client → Server)\n- `GetDashboard()` — Solicita dashboard consolidado\n- `GetServiceStatus(serviceName: string)` — Status de um serviço\n- `SubscribeToService(serviceName: string)` — Inscreve-se em updates de um serviço\n- `UnsubscribeFromService(serviceName: string)` — Cancela inscrição\n### Eventos (Server → Client)\n- `DashboardUpdate` — GatewayDashboard completo\n- `ServiceStatusChanged` — ServiceStatus atualizado\n- `Error` — Mensagem de erro",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST — ChatHub Negotiate",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/hubs/chat/negotiate?negotiateVersion=1",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "hubs",
                "chat",
                "negotiate"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "negotiateVersion",
                  "value": "1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Handshake SignalR do ChatHub. Retorna connectionId e transportes disponíveis (WebSockets, ServerSentEvents, LongPolling)."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Retorna connectionId', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('connectionId');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.connectionId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Lista transportes disponíveis', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('availableTransports');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.availableTransports).to.be.an('array').with.length.greaterThan(0);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Suporta WebSockets', () => {",
                  "    const transports = pm.response.json().availableTransports;",
                  "    const ws = transports.find(t => t.transport === 'WebSockets');",
                  "    pm.expect(ws).to.not.be.undefined;",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
